Rip notes: Nothing Was Ripped

Kao has been kidnapped and you have to help him escape his capturers in this mix of 2D & 3D adventure title from Titus.

Snowboarding, jet skiing, hang gliding, and pod racing are but a few of the fun things you'll experience as you make your way through the 30 levels of fun. To help Kao there are power-ups including power gloves, turbo boosts & checkpoint markers. Collect the coins to increase your number of lives, cause your gonna needed them to help you get past the bosses and home to safety.

Grab your boxing gloves and make your way back to OZ, punching/tail whiping/jumping your way out of danger through the 5 themed worlds.